513
00:33:35,512 --> 00:33:39,278
-How else do you keep her quiet?
-l don`t know.

514
00:33:39,483 --> 00:33:41,348
Jack, l don`t know.

515
00:33:42,553 --> 00:33:43,542
Well....

516
00:33:44,388 --> 00:33:46,879
