00:37:16,569 --> 00:37:20,471
We should get back.
Lester`s gonna leave the hotel soon.

564
00:37:20,673 --> 00:37:25,872
lt`s okay. l`ve been shooting
him all week. l`m tired of it.

565
00:37:26,079 --> 00:37:30,413
l shouldn`t have told you
my weakness is going to matinees.

566
00:37:30,617 --> 00:37:34,713
l go all the time with my niece.
lt`s like playing hooky.

567
00:37:34,921 --> 00:37:37,185
