568
00:37:37,390 --> 00:37:40,188
We weren`t late.
We didn`t miss anything.

569
00:37:40,393 --> 00:37:44,454
Have another cheeseburger.
lt`s our lunch hour.

570
00:37:44,664 --> 00:37:48,691
l got everyone at the network
excited over Professor Levy.

571
00:37:48,902 --> 00:37:51,666
l have great stuff to show you later.

572
00:37:51,871 --> 00:37:53,429
Listen...

573
00:37:54,140 --> 00:37:56,165
...l brought you a present.

574
00:37:57,210 --> 00:38:01,010
Great. Now l can get rid of
my few remaining teeth.

575
00:38:08,488 --> 00:38:10,956
-Look at his face.
-A treadmill.

576
00:38:11,157 --> 00:38:15,059
-You telling me something?
-You were bored with the bicycle.

577
00:38:15,261 --> 00:38:16,728
lt`s just as boring.

578
00:38:16,930 --> 00:38:19,660
-You`re in great shape.
