585
00:38:46,292 --> 00:38:48,692
-She`s a patient.
-On this phone?

586
00:38:49,362 --> 00:38:52,559
Yeah, she`s going through a crisis.

587
00:38:52,765 --> 00:38:56,360
-Can`t the service take it?
-lt`s probably urgent.

588
00:38:56,970 --> 00:39:00,599
l`m at the gas station
down the road from your house.

589
00:39:00,807 --> 00:39:03,207
l can be there in five minutes.

590
00:39:03,409 --> 00:39:08,005
l`m going to,
unless you meet me right now.

591
00:39:08,214 --> 00:39:09,977
No, Judah.

592
00:39:10,216 --> 00:39:11,911
No, Judah.

593
00:39:13,319 --> 00:39:17,881
No. l wanna talk to you in person,
or l`m coming over.

594
00:39:34,507 --> 00:39:37,408
-Calm down, okay?
-You said we`re going away.

595
00:39:37,610 --> 00:39:40,272
l want us to be alone.
When we get back...

596
00:39:40,480 --> 00:39:43,779
...l want you to end it with Miriam.

597
00:39:43,983 --> 00:39:46,918
l can`t go on like this
and wait forever!

598
00:39:47,120 --> 00:39:50,419
-You don`t know what it`s like!
-Talk to somebody.

599
00:39:50,623 --> 00:39:54,081
-Like a therapist or somebody.
-Don`t trick me!

600
00:39:54,294 --> 00:39:56,353
Christ, l`m shaking.

601
00:39:58,598 --> 00:39:59,826
Listen...

602
00:40:01,134 --> 00:40:03,694
...l brought you a birthday present.

603
00:40:04,137 --> 00:40:07,038
l know how much you love Schubert.

604
00:40:19,886 --> 00:40:23,287
Sometimes, when there`s real love,,,

605
00:40:23,489 --> 00:40:26,014
,,,and true acknowledgment
of a mistake,,,

606
00:40:26,225 --> 00:40:28,386
,,, there can be forgiveness too,

607
00:40:28,695 --> 00:40:30,720
I know Miriam,

608
00:40:30,930 --> 00:40:34,696
Her values, her feelings,
her place among our friends,

609
00:40:34,901 --> 00:40:38,302
What choice do you have
if the woman`s gonna tell?

610
00:40:38,504 --> 00:40:42,702
You have to confess the wrong
and hope for understanding,

611
00:40:42,909 --> 00:40:45,639
I couldn`t go on living
if I didn`t feel,,,

