-Yes?
-l have a delivery of some flowers.

750
00:52:08,553 --> 00:52:11,647
Chris and you can`t agree
on your honeymoon.

751
00:52:11,857 --> 00:52:15,020
-We can agree on something.
-We don`t disagree.

752
00:52:15,227 --> 00:52:17,923
lt`s just that l told Chris...

753
00:52:18,129 --> 00:52:21,621
...l wanna go someplace warm
that has beaches.

754
00:52:21,833 --> 00:52:25,325
But l also want to do
things like, maybe, hike.

755
00:52:25,804 --> 00:52:28,932
-l hadn`t thought of Australia.
-No, not there.

756
00:52:29,140 --> 00:52:33,304
We should go where we wanted
to go in the first place.

757
00:52:33,512 --> 00:52:37,812
-Where did you want to go?
-We wanted to go to ltaly.

758
00:52:38,016 --> 00:52:39,813
Dad, it`s Jack.

759
00:52:40,252 --> 00:52:42,652
-He`s on the phone.
-Who?

760
00:52:43,355 --> 00:52:46,119
-Jack.
