770
00:53:13,652 --> 00:53:17,679
l`m telling you, it`s like
the whole thing never existed.

771
00:53:17,889 --> 00:53:21,450
lt`s a small burglary, nothing more.

772
00:53:22,027 --> 00:53:25,986
So go on back to your life,
and put it behind you.

773
00:53:27,532 --> 00:53:29,261
l can`t speak.

774
00:53:30,201 --> 00:53:31,725
l need a drink.

775
00:53:31,937 --> 00:53:33,165
Jack....

776
00:53:35,040 --> 00:53:38,032
What am l gonna do?
l`ve got guests here now.

777
00:53:46,117 --> 00:53:48,449
God have mercy on us.

778
00:54:30,219 --> 00:54:34,178
-Mom, you said Mary had acupuncture.
-She`s tried it.

779
00:54:34,390 --> 00:54:38,326
